wikipedia_page.main: Simon Godfrey is an Anglican priest who currently serves as the Chancellor of St Paul's Pro-Cathedral in Valletta, Malta.

response: As of 7 January 2018, the current Chancellor is Simon Godfrey (since 2009).
Simon Godfrey (born 18 October 1980) is a former Australian rules footballer who played for the Melbourne Demons in the Australian Football League (AFL).
